text: Ainhoa Artolazábal Royo (born 6 March 1972) is a road cyclist from Spain. She represented her nation at the 1992 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:Spanish female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Spain Category:Living people Category:People from Tolosa Category:1972 births
